id: pm-8uhf
title: "GH #267/#271/#272 follow-up: lifecycle automation, logical dependency validation, read format parity"
description: "GitHub audit refresh found broader open reports not safe to bundle into PR #266 after the focused guardrail and small UX fixes: #267 auto-unblock blocked_by dependencies after blocker closure, #271 detect logical circular dependencies involving blocked_by and definition_of_ready/free-text readiness, and #272 unify --format support across read-only commands. Duplicate check: pm search found no canonical open items for these exact GitHub issues. These require separate design/testing because they alter lifecycle automation, validation semantics, and command output contracts."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 2
tags: []
created_at: "2026-06-18T00:15:12.340Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-18T06:04:29.073Z"
author: codex-audit-agent
parent: pm-mpbb
resolution: "Auto-unblock, lifecycle logical-cycle detection, read-command format parity, and orphaned path diagnostics implemented with SDK contracts/docs/tests."
expected_result: pm CLI provides safer lifecycle/context primitives and consistent agent-readable read output contracts.
actual_result: "Targeted tests, full coverage, manual temp smoke, contracts, changelog, audit, telemetry, and Sentry gate passed."
