  "2026-06-18T04:54:50.530Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Orientation evidence: bootstrap passed (npm install -g ., pm 2026.6.17, node v25.9.0, pnpm 10.33.4, pnpm build); gh pr list found no open PRs; gh issue list showed open #267/#271/#272/#273 plus older backlog; pnpm audit --audit-level moderate found no known vulnerabilities; pnpm outdated --recursive failed only because docs/examples/policy-restricted-extension has no lockfile. Duplicate check: pm search found pm-8uhf canonical for #267/#271/#272 and no open #273-specific item, so GH #273 is tracked here as adjacent validate UX."
  "2026-06-18T04:55:10.068Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Implementation note: attempted pm update pm-8uhf --status in_progress after claim, but update reported a lock conflict owned by the same author. No force override used per repository rules; continuing with claim plus append-only evidence commands."
  "2026-06-18T06:03:40.185Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Verification evidence: targeted tests passed (register-list-query/close/validate); full coverage passed 4508 tests with Statements 100%, Branches 100%, Functions 100%, Lines 100%; manual temp-dir smoke passed for auto-unblock, get/search --format json, lifecycle cycle validation, and orphaned path owner rows; pnpm build, contracts:check, changelog:pm:check, pnpm audit --audit-level moderate, pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift, telemetry status, and Sentry/telemetry gate all ran. Dependency freshness: commander 15.0.0 exists but is intentionally deferred because it requires Node >=22.12.0 while pm-cli package support is Node >=20."
